The laplace transform of the periodic function $$f(t)$$ described by the curve below 
<br>$$i.e.\,\,f\left( t \right) = \left\{ {\matrix{
   {\sin \,t,} &amp; {if\left( {2n - 1} \right)\pi  &lt; t &lt; 2n\pi \left( {n = 1,2,3,...} \right)}  \cr 
   0 &amp; {otherwise\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,\,}  \cr 

 } } \right.$$ is ___________.
